text:
Mala Xiang Guo (Unicuz Chinese Cuisine stall) at Superbowl Jurong, inside FM Foodmore.

$2.38 for 100 grams and minimum spending $7. Refer to photos.

Our dinner for 2 costs $21.70.

This MLXG stall really cmi.

Staff, middle age aunty, insist cash only payment can’t PayNow (maybe ownself keep portion of takings)

Food taste mediocre, oily and sauce has lots of oil taste.

Don’t patronise

Holds a big bowling alley, a supermarket, several restaurants, a food court, a spa and a preschool. ATM for POSB and UOB are located near the Superbowl entrance. Has an open carpark with 24 hour access and ease of entry to the supermarket Sheng Siong, a Drive thru fro McDonald's and the spa.
